uk.ac.ncl.jcarlton.objects

Class AbstractCar

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ncl.jcarlton.objects.AbstractCar
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Car
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LargeCar, SmallCar

    public abstract class AbstractCar
extends java.lang.Object
implements Car

    AbstractCar

    Partial implementation of the Car interface. All of the common behaviour, shared between cars, has been implemented here. To add further specialist functionality, extend this class.
    Author:
    Jonathan Carlton
    See Also:
    Car
